h2 Import into Anki

p <em>File > Import</em>, select the file, and click <em>Open</em> 

img src="images/anki_import_dialog.png"

p Make sure the Type is <em>WaniKani</em> and the Deck is <em>WaniKani</em>

p Make sure that import option is set to "Import even if existing note has the same first field"

p Since the fields being imported are in the same order as the Note Type previously created there is no need to change the mapping.

p Click <em>Import</em>


